# Notes about id3v2

# Fields I Use
# TYER :: Year
# TIT2 :: Title
# TALB :: Album Title
# TPE1 :: Artist
# TRCK :: Track Number / Optional Total Tracks
# TCON :: Content Type (Genre)

# Common fields to delete:
# COMM : TENC : TSSE : APIC : TPE2 : TXXX : 


id3v2 -l file.mp3 # List id3 tags for file.mp3
id3v2 --TPOS "1/2" 01-* # Sets all files matching 01-* to be part of a set as 1 of 2 (As in disc 1 of 2)
id3v2 -r TSSE *.mp3 # Removes the id3v2 frame TSSE from all .mp3 files
 
